</tbody></tgroup></informaltable>

<example><title> </title><para>
<programlisting>@text { string = Tonight; 
  y_off = 1.7; x_off = -0.1; justification = centre; }</programlisting>
Display the text string "Tonight" 1.7 "units" above and 0.1 "units" to the left of the current "anchor position" and centre justified.
</para></example>

<example><title> </title><para>
<programlisting>@text { text_file = $FPA/setup/pdf/psmet/examples/example_file;
  font = "Times-Italic"; italics = yes; }</programlisting>
Display text from the file <filename><envar>$FPA</envar>/setup/pdf/psmet/examples/example_file</filename> at the current
"anchor position". The text font will be set to "Times-Italic" style using italics.
(Note that <userinput>units</userinput> is set by <link linkend='ps_display_units'>@display_units</link>, and "anchor position" is set by <link linkend='ps_anchor'>@anchor</link>.)

</para></example>
</para></sect2>
